data.description: This remodeled Craftsman bungalow has three bedrooms, and 2 1/2 baths, primary bedroom on the main level, and offers plenty of space for you and the family. Fully remodeled home, new kitchen cabinets, new bathrooms, new laminate flooring throughout the main level, new roof, new windows, new electric, and plumbing! Upon arriving you will notice a nice large, covered porch for your morning coffee, entering the home you will find a spacious sun-filled living room that flows into a separate dining space for the whole family. The kitchen has been renovated with brand-new cabinets, backsplash, and plenty of room for cooking your meals. The back door leads to a covered porch area which could easily be converted into a screened-in porch or used for family BBQ's. Most of the spacious yard is fenced creating a great area for outdoor activities and relaxation. Inside on the main level, you will find a nice-sized primary bedroom with its own on-suite bath, two separate walk-in closets, and a double vanity. The second level provides two nice-sized bedrooms, closets, and a shared Jack and Jill bathroom between the rooms. Basement provides a good amount of storage space. There is currently a parking area in front of the house but there could also be a driveway area to the left side of the home. The home also has city alley access to the back yard of the home. This home has close proximity to downtown Bristol TN, with easy access to all the amenities and entertainment options the downtown has to offer. This home offers the perfect balance of updated style, functionality, and outdoor space. It could very well be your dream home!
